    "required_age": "18",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/098dfca2ed3de7a2698317ac0c659e91.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fallout 4》由屡获殊荣的《Starfield》与《The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim》创作团队Bethesda Game Studios倾力打造。它不仅是开放世界角色扮演游戏的扛鼎之作，还夺得了包括DICE与BAFTA年度游戏在内的200余项“最佳游戏”大奖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为111号避难所唯一的幸存者，你将踏入这个被核战摧毁殆尽的世界。每一秒钟你都必须为生存而战，而你的每个决定都将让未来截然不同。按照你的方式重建文明、改变环境并拯救这片废土。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎回家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/5f0ee5a868640265a74b503bcf08747b.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/da7e75ff538d2af951852831c81a4dd3.poster.avif?t=1764687456\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/da7e75ff538d2af951852831c81a4dd3.webm?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/da7e75ff538d2af951852831c81a4dd3.mp4?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由与解放</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心体验拥有数百个地点、角色和人物的广阔开放世界。加入阵营、组建联盟或孤身闯荡，你可以遵从自己的意愿做出决定，而每个决定都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/f61e77ce3d9724671436050fb8e69e2b.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/afa303d396ab5b07cf4b570e01c6497d.poster.avif?t=1764687456\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/afa303d396ab5b07cf4b570e01c6497d.webm?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/afa303d396ab5b07cf4b570e01c6497d.mp4?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S.P.E.C.I.A.L.就是与众不同</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用S.P.E.C.I.A.L.属性系统创造出独一无二的角色。从数百种辅助能力中精心挑选，无论是能言善辩的外交家、行踪诡秘的狙击手还是身穿动力装甲的人形坦克，你都能够找到最适合自己的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/da771dcb647188df70c032e9932dfc3d.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/c4b79e9975ef388466a328d1c76d619f.poster.avif?t=1764687456\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/c4b79e9975ef388466a328d1c76d619f.webm?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/c4b79e9975ef388466a328d1c76d619f.mp4?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集与建造</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过全新方式进行收集、制作与定制，打造包括护甲、武器与食物在内的数千种物品，并在联邦各处建造与管理多个定居点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/47c4858932f9691b9d6cca3c7d0efc68.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/526fe07fd8291fa35d6023408543307c.poster.avif?t=1764687456\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/526fe07fd8291fa35d6023408543307c.webm?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/526fe07fd8291fa35d6023408543307c.mp4?t=1764687456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式第一人称/第三人称战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用动态避难所科技辅助瞄准系统（V.A.T.S.），在战斗中以电影演出般的表现形式减缓时间流逝并瞄准敌人；或者选择通过实时枪战的方式亲自掌控战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/377160/extras/faecf43e9696b14c9b9876eec080c515.avif?t=1764687456\" width=1560 height=194 /></span></p>",
